                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-02-17T22:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 17, 1913—10 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. Department’s February 17, 2 a.m. The policy indicated in the instruction
                    following the quotation was adopted some days ago and is being and will be
                    pursued.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
